visualizeR
==========

* New built-in datasets: DJF global mean sea-level pressure, temperature and total precipitation from NCEP/NCAR reanalysis and NCEP-CFSv2 hindcast
* New function for reliability diagram, implementing the approach in Weisheimer and Palmer 2014 (DOI: 10.1098/rsif.2013.1162) 
* Other minor bug fixes and enhancements